text: Rana Sherif Ahmed (; born 20 July 1994) is an Egyptian tennis player. Sherif Ahmed On 8 November 2010, she reached her best singles ranking of world number 1110. On 8 November 2010, she peaked at world number 982 in the doubles rankings.
